&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Although we can use &apos;Analyze table partition &apos; to update the totalSize,rawDataSize or rowCount, it&apos;s unresonable for normal SQL to throw NumberFormatException for Empty totalSize.We should fix the empty case when readHiveStats.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Here is the empty case:&lt;br/&gt;
 &lt;span class=&quot;image-wrap&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/attachment/12988849/12988849_screenshot-1.png&quot; style=&quot;border: 0px solid black&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
